cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.ET

The paper discusses learning in hierarchical networks of leaky integrate-and-fire neurons, which is a topic closely related to neural networks and machine learning. Therefore, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also addresses issues related to optimization and dynamics, which are relevant to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of neuromorphic devices suggests a possible connection to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.ET (Emerging Technologies).
